headline.print_headline: Barry Diller-Backed Aereo Raises Additional $34 Million
headline.main: Barry Diller-Backed Aereo Raises Additional $34 Million

lead_paragraph: Aereo Inc, the Barry Diller-backed online television venture that is facing a legal battle from four major broadcasters said it had raised $34 million from its new round of financing.
